 Langkah-Langkah Pembuatan 
✅ 1. Buat Proyek Flutter 
bash
 
flutter create diary_app
cd diary_app
 
 
✅ 2. Tambahkan依赖 Hive di pubspec.yaml 

Buka file pubspec.yaml dan tambahkan dependency: 
yaml
 
dependencies:
  flutter:
    sdk: flutter
  hive: ^2.2.3
  hive_flutter: ^1.1.0
 
 

Kemudian jalankan: 
bash
 
flutter pub get
 
 
✅ 3. Buat Model Catatan (Note) 

Buat file note.dart di folder lib/models/: 
dart
 
    
// lib/models/note.dart
import 'package:hive/hive.dart';

part 'note.g.dart';

@HiveType(typeId: 0)
class Note extends HiveObject {
  @HiveField(0)
  final String title;

  @HiveField(1)
  final String content;

  @HiveField(2)
  final DateTime createdAt;

  Note(this.title, this.content, this.createdAt);
}
 
 

    ⚠️ Catatan: Anda perlu menjalankan flutter pub run build_runner build untuk generate file note.g.dart.
    Tambahkan dependency di pubspec.yaml: 
    yaml

    dev_dependencies:
      build_runner: ^2.3.3
      hive_generator: ^2.0.1
     
     
     

✅ 4. Inisialisasi Hive di main.dart 
dart
 
   
// lib/main.dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'package:hive_flutter/hive_flutter.dart';
import 'screens/home_screen.dart';

void main() async {
  // Inisialisasi Hive
  await Hive.initFlutter();
  Hive.registerAdapter(NoteAdapter()); // Register adapter
  runApp(const MyApp());
}
 
 
